definitions.definition: A simple dessert made by cooking sweetened milk with cornstarch and vanilla .
A dish, eaten in the Middle Ages, generally consisting of chicken (or sometimes capon or fish ), milk or almond milk , rice , and sugar .

main_definition: A simple dessert made by cooking sweetened milk with cornstarch and vanilla .
